PRIME MINISTER'S SECRETARIAT
228.
1. Shri Jagjivan Ram will relinquish charge of the
Ministry of Communications and take charge of the Ministries
of Transport and Railways from Shri Lal Bahadur Shastri.
2.
Shri Raj Bahadur, Minister in the Ministry of
Communications, will hold charge of the Ministry of
Communications, except the Department of Civil Aviation.
Shri H. V. Pataskar, Minister of Legal Affairs, will
hold additional charge of the Department of Civil Aviation.
Sa/- J. Nehru.
5-12-1956.
